Title: A-Gas R404A rental cylinder 11kg
Description: This A-Gas 11kg rental cylinder contains R-404A, a HFC blend suitable as a replacement for R502 and R-22 in low and medium temperature refrigeration applications. With a GWP above 2500, the use of R-404A is now prohibited in new equipment and restricted in pre-existing equipment while reclaimed R-404A is still permitted until 2030 for servicing equipment already running and is therefore an option for those with systems above 40T CO2 equivalent (approximately 10kgs of R-404A).

Title: A-Gas R23 rental cylinder 8.5kg
Description: This A-Gas 8.5kg rental cylinder contains R-23, a suitable replacement for R-13 and R503 in very low temperature refrigeration. R-23 can also used as a clean fire suppressant, replacing Halon 1301.
